{
    "attributes": {
        "action": "Make the destruction or scrapping of UK military medals a criminal offence",
        "additional_details": "Scrapping or damaging medals erases personal and national history. These honours deserve legal protection to stop their permanent loss for furure generations.",
        "background": "Make it a criminal offence to destroy or scrap officially issued UK military medals. Rising silver prices and a lucrative collectors' market mean medals are being melted down for profit, engraved names erased and service details and irreplaceable records of those who served destroyed forever.",
